  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541050/extras/ac5c438e6aa6fc4c5d04754300aea8c4.webp?t=1762827014\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I thought I would wake up in my own bed, like I always do...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But instead, I found myself awakening in a dusty cave, with a peculiar young girl staring at me from the side!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Good morning! Nice to meet you, Master—!\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"You have been chosen by this dungeon as its master!\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Join me in managing the mightiest underground dungeon!!\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I have no choice but to obey that girl,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and embark on the journey of dungeon management...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541050/extras/8a256d744f57566984667fd73673b995.webp?t=1762827014\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rookie Adventurer 「Rookie(Alias)」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541050/extras/a20d5ab6541389e7d882833e38e10967.avif?t=1762827014\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paladin「Holy(Alias)」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541050/extras/bbb668a68dd86c45b582523b7d1d6da9.avif?t=1762827014\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Veteran Thief「Rogue(Alias)」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541050/extras/c4107820a3406adc9be25947380f620c.avif?t=1762827014\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The former angel「Reyla」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541050/extras/750646405cbb6eca641bb401c2c0e2e0.avif?t=1762827014\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541050/extras/fd7d65b8fb1f040982258ffbdafb5004.webp?t=1762827014\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple tower defense game (RPG)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Option to skip through dialogues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full-screen mode support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable keys/gamepad compatibility</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Window hiding functionality</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogue history available for review</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
